==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Tagliacotain
<hw>Tagl`ia*co"tain</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <fld>(Surg.)</fld>
<def>Of or pertaining to <xex>Tagliacozzi</xex>, a Venetian surgeon;
<as>as, the <ex>Tagliacotian</ex> operation, a method of rhinoplasty
described by him</as>.</def> <altsp>[Also <asp>Taliacotian</asp>, and
<asp>Tagliacozzian</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Taglioni</ent>⟦br⟧
